	(text_box "The 'G5V-1' module requires a 4.5V to 5.5V supply and can switch a wide range of positive and negative voltages.\n\nThe '74LVC1G3157' module requires a 2.5 V to 5.5 V supply and can switch voltages from 0 V to +Vsupply.\n\nVBUS (+5V) is selected by default, as this programmer should work better with the 'G5V-1' module. If you prefer to use the '74LVC1G3157' module and VBUS never drops below VTG, then the default setting can remain unchanged. Otherwise, please reposition the jumper to select VTG."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 111.76 25.4 0)
		(size 127 49.53)
		(stroke
			(width 0)
			(type default)
			(color 0 0 255 1)
		)
		(fill
